OL,3,CTrial date set for man who denies
OL,4,Ckilling Karen Cummings
OL,6,FA trial date has been set for the man
OL,7,Fwho denies killing children's nurse
OL,8,FKaren Cummings in Co Down in 2024.
OL,10,FThe mother of two was shot dead in her
OL,11,FBanbridge home on the 14th of December.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, 44-year-old Kevin
OL,14,FMcGuigan with an address at Maghaberry
OL,15,Fprison appeared in the dock in Belfast
OL,16,Fand when the charge of manslaughter
OL,17,Fwas put to him he replied not guilty.
OL,19,FMr McGuigan also pleaded not guilty to
OL,20,Fa number of firearm offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
