OL,3,CTrial date set for man who denies
OL,4,Ckilling Karen Cummings
OL,6,FHis co-accused, 34-year-old Glen King
OL,7,Fof Magilligan prison, is facing a
OL,8,Fmanslaughter charge.
OL,10,FThe court heard Mr King intends to
OL,11,Fmount a legal application in the case
OL,12,Fagainst him.
OL,14,FDetails of what happened inside the
OL,15,FLaurel Heights property were not given
OL,16,Fin court today.
OL,18,FKaren's family sat in the dock.
